Refactored xcode project to a framework

- Added unit testing for all methods
- AddedUI extension examples to README
- Added week to isInCurrent method in DateExtensions
- Added animated argument to scale method in UIViewExtensions
- Tabs used instead of spaces in all files for a cleaner code
